# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Licensed IBO content — reviewed locally / applied to Supabase, NEVER committed.
# This repo is PUBLIC; committing verbatim IB guide/markscheme/paper text or the
# source PDFs would republish copyrighted material regardless of license.
# The STRUCTURAL migration (20260701_ib_assessment_catalog.sql — tables only, no
# IBO content) and the calibration fixture (facts only) STAY tracked.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# licensed catalog seeds (verbatim descriptors/prose)
supabase/migrations/*_ib_*_seed.sql
# ingestion records contain verbatim descriptors/prose
docs/ib-ingestion/
# uploaded AA guide + question papers + markschemes (source docs)
/Mathematics*.pdf
# licensed IB document libraries (guides, subject reports, core docs) — never commit
/IB DOCUMENTS/
/IB SUBJECT GUIDES/
/IB SUBJECT REPORTS/

# Licensed IB specimen papers + teacher support material (out-of-band)
/IB SPECIMEN PAPERS/
/IB TEACHER SUPPORT MATERIAL/

# Third-party reference/revision materials — used for SCOPE-ONLY survey during
# course authoring (facts are free; their expression is not). Copyrighted
# content owned by other sites; NEVER commit (this repo is PUBLIC).
/Bananaomics 2022/
/LitCharts/
/LitLearn/
/SaveMyExams - Notes/
/StudyIB/
/ThinkIB/
/ibGenius/
/revision-town-2024/
/theoryofknowledge.net/
